# Dropbox cloud backup (optional). When unset, the cloud-backup feature is
# inert and hidden from the UI. Create a Scoped-access, App-folder Dropbox app
# (scopes: account_info.read, files.content.write, files.metadata.read) and put
# its App key here. Register the redirect URIs origin + BASE_URL, e.g.
# https://app.sightlines.art/ and http://localhost:5173/.
VITE_DROPBOX_CLIENT_ID=

# Cloud-backup scheduler timing overrides (milliseconds). Optional — omit to use
# the defaults (settle 180000 = 3 min, min interval 720000 = 12 min). Mainly for
# e2e/tests that need faster cycles.
# VITE_CLOUD_BACKUP_SETTLE_MS=
# VITE_CLOUD_BACKUP_MIN_INTERVAL_MS=
